==Description==
The '''Macho Brace''' is a type of [[Held Items|Held Item]] that can only be equipped to Pokémon [[File:Pokérus (Contagious).png|40px]] infected with [[Pokérus]].

==Details==
Raises the EV gain of the Pokémon holding the Item by 100%.

